channel.title: Need help!
channel.description:
Dear moparians,
Im coding my own prjoect for almost 2 years now. But now i wanna host it but whenever i try i cant get money to paypal. Please can you donate or give me some easy job to get some money to buy my own vps ! Im now very hopeless but im really tired of waiting and waiting. Please PM me if you could donate me some cash or give some easy job such as coding server/client or doing some graphic work. My skype is: ylar.l so you can add me there or PM here! Unfortunately i didn't know right section for this post so i posted it here. Please move it if its needed!
Thank you for reading!
